OL,3,CMisogyny among pupils a 'ticking time
OL,4,Cbomb' in UK schools, warns union
OL,6,FA "masculinity crisis" is brewing in
OL,7,FUK schools with the number of
OL,8,Fmisogynistic incidents against female
OL,9,Fteachers on the rise.
OL,11,FA survey by teachers union NASUWT
OL,12,Ffound 23.4% of female staff members
OL,13,Fwere subjected to misogyny from a
OL,14,Fpupil in the last year - up from 22.2%
OL,15,Fthe year before and 17.4% in 2023.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
