OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775347371
OL,3,CMisogyny among pupils a 'ticking time
OL,4,Cbomb' in UK schools, warns union
OL,6,FSharing their experiences, one teacher
OL,7,Fsaid a student had made naked images
OL,8,Fof her and others using AI, while
OL,9,Fothers described being called
OL,10,Fmisogynistic names regularly and being
OL,11,Fmeowed at by male students.
OL,13,FOther survey respondents recounted
OL,14,Fbeing called a "f*****g slag" by
OL,15,Fstudents, having sexual noises and
OL,16,Fgestures made at them, and being asked
OL,17,Fif they were on their period.
OL,26,@vD@POUvD@]O]
