OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775347371
OL,3,CMisogyny among pupils a 'ticking time
OL,4,Cbomb' in UK schools, warns union
OL,6,FMany female teachers said pupils were
OL,7,Fmisogynistic towards them when they
OL,8,Fattempted to address their behaviour
OL,9,For they weren't listened to because of
OL,10,Ftheir gender.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,F"We have a masculinity crisis brewing
OL,18,Fin our schools," NASUWT general
OL,19,Fsecretary Matt Wrack said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
