PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775347371
OL,3,CMisogyny among pupils a 'ticking time
OL,4,Cbomb' in UK schools, warns union
OL,6,F"Teachers desperately need increased
OL,7,Fsupport to deal with this new frontier
OL,8,Fof behaviour management ` it affects
OL,9,Fthe wellbeing of everyone in the
OL,10,Fclassroom.
OL,12,F"This generation of teachers faces an
OL,13,Funprecedented task that requires
OL,14,Furgent action from policymakers."
OL,16,FMore than one in five of more than
OL,17,F5,000 teachers who completed the
OL,18,Fsurvey said they had been subjected to
OL,19,Fsexist, racist or homophobic language
OL,20,Ffrom a pupil in the past year.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@aO]
