OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775347371
OL,3,CMisogyny among pupils a 'ticking time
OL,4,Cbomb' in UK schools, warns union
OL,6,FOne teacher said she faced misogyny on
OL,7,Fa daily basis, including abusive
OL,8,Flanguage.
OL,10,F"Have had boys joke about raping girls
OL,11,Fin front of me and laughed about it
OL,12,Fwhen challenged," the teacher said.
OL,14,F"Parents have told me if I can't
OL,15,Fhandle teenage boys then I need to
OL,16,F'work in a f*****g nursery'."
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@QO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
