OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775347371
OL,3,CMisogyny among pupils a 'ticking time
OL,4,Cbomb' in UK schools, warns union
OL,6,FTeachers need mandatory training that
OL,7,Fhelps them identify, challenge and
OL,8,Fsafely de-escalate behaviour rooted in
OL,9,Fonline radicalisation, sexism and
OL,10,Fhate, Wrack said.
OL,12,F"If female teachers are reporting that
OL,13,Fthey cannot contain gender-based
OL,14,Faggression in their classrooms ` and
OL,15,Fthat is exactly what they are telling
OL,16,FNASUWT ` then we have a ticking time
OL,17,Fbomb on our hands," Wrack said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
