CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775347371
OL,3,CMisogyny among pupils a 'ticking time
OL,4,Cbomb' in UK schools, warns union
OL,6,F"These pupils are the same boys and
OL,7,Fyoung men who will go on to be
OL,8,Fhusbands, fathers, and colleagues in
OL,9,Fthe workplace.
OL,11,F"They may eventually develop influence
OL,12,Fin the public sphere. We must help
OL,13,Fthem and their victims ` including
OL,14,Fteachers ` before it is too late."
OL,16,FWrack called for social media and AI
OL,17,Fcompanies to be held responsible for
OL,18,Fmisinformation spreading on their
OL,19,Fplatforms, and face sanctions if they
OL,20,Fdon't address the issues.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
