OL,3,CMisogyny among pupils a 'ticking time
OL,4,Cbomb' in UK schools, warns union
OL,6,FIt comes as the government considers
OL,7,Fmeasures to limit the social media use
OL,8,Fof under-16s, with Prime Minister Keir
OL,9,FStarmer promisinh to "fight" social
OL,10,Fmedia firms over addictive content.
OL,12,FTeachers in the National Education
OL,13,FUnion have also warned that pupils are
OL,14,Fbeing influenced by racist and
OL,15,Fmisogynistic extreme social media
OL,16,Fcontent.
OL,26,@qD@VOUqD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
