PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775347371
OL,3,CMisogyny among pupils a 'ticking time
OL,4,Cbomb' in UK schools, warns union
OL,6,F"Misogynistic views are not innate,
OL,7,Fthey are learned, and we are committed
OL,8,Fto using every possible tool to
OL,9,Fachieve our mission of halving
OL,10,Fviolence against women and girls," a
OL,11,FDepartment for Education spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"Our updated RSHE guidance is designed
OL,15,Fto make sure all young people can
OL,16,Fidentify positive role models, and we
OL,17,Fare providing resources to support
OL,18,Fteachers to recognise the signs of
OL,19,Fincel ideologies so we can intervene
OL,20,Feffectively, including through the
OL,21,FEducate Against Hate programme.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
